                    "description": "The URL of a publicly accessible tiled raster service.",
                    "pattern": "https?:\\/\\/(www\\.)?[-a-zA-Z0-9@:%._\\+~#=]{1,256}\\.[a-zA-Z0-9()]{1,6}([-a-zA-Z0-9()@:%_\\+.~#?&//=\\{\\}]*)",
                    "title": "Custom Layer URL",
